{"tid":1751141,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"西九4小龍投票率全港最高 最年輕選區天恒邨70%人投票","createTime":"2019-11-24T16:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T19:47:26.000Z","uid":211782,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d98f792544477601a477c3541b0bacb36ddd01e9","tid":1751141,"uid":211782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:12:42.000Z","msg":"全港區議會選舉投票率突破7成，上屆投票率最高的票站深水埗區「荔枝角中」、即西九四小龍的最終投票率高達81.9%，較上屆65.3%，高出17個百分點，投票率之高超過沙田「第一城」的81.3%，暫時是已知票站的全港最高。「荔枝角中」共有8,704名選名，7,128人投票，較上屆多2500人投票。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191124/60306112?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191124%2F60306112%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=ZQL1o3idxa%2FDGLG1XyUJb3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=d70952c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191124%2F60306112%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=46730d0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191124/60306112?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"539cf81330c3ba3bed340747073f0109563918e8","tid":1751141,"uid":211782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:13:30.000Z","msg":"4小龍竟然贏咗第一城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de9b568f9f0d4296b0a98af953b8cd66afd2c24","tid":1751141,"uid":48,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T16:14:16.000Z","msg":"天恒係咪百羽"},{"pi